title: 用forge裝好mod....開minecraft出現問題！
author: danny789741
txt_content:
開minecraft出現：   A list of ID conflicts has been written to 
the file `IDConflicts.txt' in your minecraft directory.

我入minecraft開`IDConflicts.txt' 入面有：
#Blocks
960: dimanchor from ImmibisCore - blockTradeBoothStorage from tradeboothmod
3972: calclavia:multiPart from CalclaviaCore - aluminumWire from GalacticraftCore
Suggested Ranges: 2529-2999 (471 IDs), 422-699 (278 IDs), 3522-3767 (246 IDs)



求解決方法！
